incident_updates.body: Update : Our technical teams are still working on a definitive fix to implement it with the aim to avoid the problem in the future.
Update : A fix has been deployed, we are monitoring the ticket to confirm the resolution.

Start time : 23/10/2023 00:00 UTC Service impact : The certificate of conformity for deliveries of Baremetal servers (except SYS and KS servers) is no longer issued automatically. Ongoing actions : Our teams are working to resolve the problem. Certificates will be added as soon as possible. Workaround : However, you can request your certificate from the support teams.
